strings: <voice_0x010010C7><se_def>*: Hold me, where do you think I'm going?
<voice_0x010010C8><se_def>*: I never thought people would turn you into such an immoral, ignorant, and unscrupulous person. That is, one to one!
<voice_0x010010C9><se_low>January: Hilarious, the crowd! We'll see! That doesn't surprise us, does it? Then ask if you have tried it!
<voice_0x010010CA><se_def>China: I don't think you need notes. Walking is not a foreign word for us.
<voice_0x010010CB><se_high>Accuracy: Pardon me! We never did anything to earn this little terror. we travel alot
<voice_0x010010CC><se_low>King of tricks: Call us! Ashamed of what I said before I could!
<voice_0x010010CD><se_low>King of tricks: At least tell us what it is that you don't like about us.
<voice_0x010010CE><se_def>*: I don't care what you say, I won't let you go, I won't tell anybody but look at your evidence!
<voice_0x010010CF><se_def>*: you are the worst! Sounds weird if you ask me!
<voice_0x010010D0><se_def>*: Don't complain when you meet people like monsters!
<voice_0x010010D1><se_def>*: Good luck not getting caught! Get out of here before you change your mind!
